{"tid":1235351,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"罷緊工嘅你，返緊工嘅你，唔撚知做乜嘅你，請做靜觀！","createTime":"2019-06-17T06:11:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T05:57:49.000Z","uid":13754,"like":63,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"b2642711f339e91737477e8a41ef9ebee983d38b","tid":1235351,"uid":13754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T06:11:49.000Z","msg":"要打持久戰，我哋要有健康嘅精神狀態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果唔係就好易做錯判斷，咁就變豬隊友嘞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢兩個禮拜我哋吸收咗太多真嘅假嘅資訊，參加咗好多人行動，我哋需要休息一陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我好想喺度推動大家一齊，每日做靜觀（Mindfulness）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咩係靜觀可以睇以下呢段片<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-LHT_2sgMtg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-LHT_2sgMtg&d=goC%2B%2BwCxwRgX8SEPTes0u1tn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=51327b4f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-LHT_2sgMtg</a><br />\n<br />\n有研究指出，有持續進行靜觀習慣嘅人，大腦嘅灰質會增加，對人嘅同理心，耐性都會改善<br />\n<br />\n另外一個重點，係可以改善睡眠質素，令身體健康啲！<br />\n<br />\n呢度另外有一篇長文講靜觀<br />\n<a href=\"https://treehole.hk/靜觀-一文爲你解通/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftreehole.hk%2F%E9%9D%9C%E8%A7%80-%E4%B8%80%E6%96%87%E7%88%B2%E4%BD%A0%E8%A7%A3%E9%80%9A%2F&d=goC%2B%2BwCxwRgX8SEPTes0u1tn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=d7b25fc3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://treehole.hk/靜觀-一文爲你解通/</a><br />\n<br />\n咁靜觀點做呢？<br />\n其實真係好簡單<br />\n1. Set好Timer做1分鐘 (可以唔止1分鐘，但建議啱啱開始可以由每日1分鐘做起）<br />\n2. 坐好，雙手放喺大腿上<br />\n3. 合埋雙眼<br />\n4. 慢慢深呼吸，將注意力放喺<br />\n-- 鼻哥窿上面，感受下吸氣同呼氣鼻哥窿嘅感覺，或者<br />\n-- 腹部隆起同收縮嘅感覺<br />\n5. 重複4. 直到Timer響<br />\n<br />\n當你深呼吸嘅時候，可能會諗起好多嘢Side track你嘅注意力，但唔需要緊張，只要當你察覺到自己分咗心嘅時候，慢慢返返去鼻哥窿或者腹部嘅感覺就可以嘞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家趁而家放飯，留一分鐘時間畀自己做一做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pEcn2yu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpEcn2yu.jpg&h=96ab9e9c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"727cc6220bb95d79e7daaafca4d70228dc3f5170","tid":1235351,"uid":13754,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T06:11:57.000Z","msg":"咁係我叫大家去做去練習，咁我又好簡單講下我做成點<br />\n<br />\n我係前年開始知呢樣嘢，嗰時我經歷咗一啲好大嘅問題，有啲Depress，個人情緒好唔穩定，同埋好容易焦慮<br />\n<br />\n當我去每日都預啲時間（我有空檔就做5分鐘）畀自己去深呼吸嘅時候，發覺個人會覺得平靜咗舒服咗，同埋會對啲事冇咁負面<br />\n<br />\n人一冇咁負面就開始識諗解決辦法，或者識得去接受啲嘢<br />\n<br />\n我都有去14年嘅雨革，嗰時我係好暴躁同好神經質，好容易會受人分化<br />\n<br />\n但今年我覺得自己係理性咗，對人有多咗同理心！<br />\n<br />\n我女朋友都話我同兩年前唔同咗好多，希望我哋都可以Be a better man!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa0b228cbacd61b2f0b3da2947ba98fd5fd29207","tid":1235351,"uid":13754,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T07:17:25.000Z","msg":"三點三，嚟個深呼吸先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0688f46c5c29fcbc56a57c17cc6509dd0b344bee","tid":1235351,"uid":140354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T07:19:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb07e9c65ad0852206f73e1df42a5289c34da600","tid":1235351,"uid":13754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T09:11:42.000Z","msg":"就收工嘞，深呼吸先執嘢走<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b8d6fab004e454a269d13d396646fbabaaca084","tid":1235351,"uid":248275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T09:12:57.000Z","msg":"將注意力擺鼻窿上面 以為係鼻頭"},{"pid":"500eaf18ddd258ea4e55cbe012306735ba5286cf","tid":1235351,"uid":13754,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4b8d6fab004e454a269d13d396646fbabaaca084","tid":1235351,"uid":248275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T09:12:57.000Z","msg":"將注意力擺鼻窿上面 以為係鼻頭"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"